name: Validate CRUD functionality related to Articles

elements.name: As a logged in user, I should be able to create an article

steps.name: User clicks on sign in link
User enters 'test1223@gmail.com' and 'test@123'
User signs in
User should be logged in with 'testuserfollow'
User clicks on New Post link
User fills all the article creation details with title 'Article Check' description 'Article about' content 'This is a sample' and tags 'demo'
User clicks button Publish Article
User validates the published article for user 'testuserfollow'
User clicks on Home link
User clicks on Global feed
User should be able to see article created
